10:
Ahaha! Did I scare you? Got you
good, right?
14:
Tarha... I get that you love pranking
people, but you shouldn't go
overboard, okay?
29:
Sorry for all the fuss. We were only
supposed to be foraging, but Tarha
can't help himself...
33:
Hohoho! It's all right. The lad's not
'urting anyone.
55:
T-Tarha?! Didn't I just tell you not to
go overboard!
60:
Bleeegh! You gotta catch me if you
want me to stop! Ahaha!
66:
Sorry for the scare, Regitare!
Tarha, get back here!
72:
The lad loves his pranks, eh? I
thought me 'eart was going to stop
for a moment there.
80: Oh! That's right, I forgot again!
85:
What? So you're actually dead, old
man?
90: Well, that was a quick game of tag!
97:
Anyway, if you're dead, then that
means you're the same as me!
101:
Hmm... Your situation's a tad
different, but I suppose you could
say that.
104:
When did you die? Since you're all
bones, it must've been a long time
ago! Longer than me!
107: I wonder... I don't rightly remember.
110:
When you live long enough, you
start to forget all the things from
way back when.
114:
Ahaha, you just said "live long
enough" even though you're dead!
123:
If even you don't remember your
past... does that mean everyone
eventually forgets?
126:
Old man, doesn't it bother you that
you don't remember?
133:
If it does, you just need to take a
closer gander at everything around
you now.
136:
That's how these young ones here
saved me.
149:
Hohohoho! It's a little embarrassing
to be told that so frankly!
160: Sorry for the wait! Let's dig in!
168:
Mm, that's good! Your cooking
always hits the spot, Alk!
176:
Oh! Nimbus! Stella! I picked these
mushrooms! You should have some!
190:
Aren't they? If you want more, I'll go
pick more!
193:
We just started eating them. You
don't need to go rushing off yet.
198:
Haha, I see you're full of energy
today. It's fine to play pranks, so long
as you do it in moderation.
210: Ahaha, yeah, don't worry about me!
213:
I just realized how much fun I'm
having right now, that's all!
